title: New Girl - Complete Season 3 S03 - 720p - x265
description:
As for the first (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/15637341) and second (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/15724367) seasons, don't expect the full quality of beautiful HD but rather "better than SD for ~half the size".

Converted from https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/13900123/New_Girl_S03_Season_3_Complete_1080p_WEB-DL_[HWD] and let's be honest, this release was a mess. Seriously. Why keeping the F0x ads ?

So, I converted the audio to AAC 2.0, removed those AWEFUL pre and post-roll F0x ads on each episodes, added and resynced the subtitles to match (so, the subtitles in the wild won't work, probably).

Anyway, as always, don't hesitate to give me any suggestion.
I will (probably) do the remaining seasons in the coming weeks
